   only from the Parque Internacional La Amistad in Costa. Rica side. It
   can be distinguished by the long peduncles up to 6.5 cm long, pendant
   flowers with green petals and indumentum of roughened trichomes. A key
   to other species of Blakea with pendulous flowers and connivent petals
